Section 23.787 Baggage and Cargo Compartments 



Section 23.787 would be revised by extending the present requirements for cargo compartments to baggage compartments.
As proposed, future baggage compartments on all airplane categories would be required to: Be placarded for their
maximum weight capacity; have a means to prevent the baggage from shifting; and have a means to protect controls, wiring,
